      columnNumber: 7
    }
  }, "Molly Pitcher Clubs There were many anti-Prohibition movements besides the Women's Organization for National Prohibition Reform. The Association Against the Prohibition Amendment had female chapters they named Molly Pitcher Clubs. This club never gained much national recognition, and likely did not grow very large.[16]"), /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("div", {
